1
00:00:13,740 --> 00:00:14,460
It's you.

2
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:28,540
Hand over the Fushi Mirror.

3
00:00:29,500 --> 00:00:30,940
Or I'll kill her.

4
00:00:31,460 --> 00:00:32,980
Don't worry about me. Run!

5
00:00:33,540 --> 00:00:34,500
You really think

6
00:00:34,500 --> 00:00:36,380
I care about her?

7
00:00:45,660 --> 00:00:46,540
Stop!

8
00:01:01,800 --> 00:01:04,720
[Immortal Beyond Dust]
[Episode 22]

9
00:01:21,060 --> 00:01:21,900
I'm sorry.

10
00:01:22,660 --> 00:01:23,500
It's all because of me that...

11
00:01:23,500 --> 00:01:25,460
I handed the mirror over myself.

12
00:01:25,780 --> 00:01:27,260
It has nothing to do with you.

13
00:01:28,340 --> 00:01:30,380
Don't flatter yourself.

14
00:01:34,180 --> 00:01:35,180
I'm useless.

15
00:01:36,660 --> 00:01:37,780
I lost

16
00:01:38,740 --> 00:01:40,300
the Fushi Mirror again.

17
00:01:47,500 --> 00:01:48,660
Overestimating yourself.

18
00:01:48,900 --> 00:01:50,500
You actually dared target
the Fushi Mirror?

19
00:01:50,980 --> 00:01:51,940
Do you realize

20
00:01:52,460 --> 00:01:55,060
the power of Xieyun is far beyond
what the Shadow Clan can handle?

21
00:01:59,460 --> 00:02:00,140
No.

22
00:02:00,980 --> 00:02:02,420
No matter the cost,

23
00:02:02,740 --> 00:02:04,140
we must obtain the Fushi Mirror.

24
00:02:05,180 --> 00:02:05,980
Back then,

25
00:02:07,460 --> 00:02:09,940
it was my fault that my brother
and the Shadow Clan warriors

26
00:02:10,100 --> 00:02:11,060
were sealed away.

27
00:02:11,780 --> 00:02:14,980
And it's my fault our people
were left displaced.

28
00:02:15,540 --> 00:02:16,900
From that moment,

29
00:02:18,340 --> 00:02:19,820
I swore an oath.

30
00:02:20,780 --> 00:02:21,900
I would

31
00:02:22,780 --> 00:02:24,340
take back everything I'd lost!

32
00:02:27,780 --> 00:02:29,260
I only learned today

33
00:02:29,500 --> 00:02:31,100
how much you've been carrying.

34
00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:34,140
I don't need your pity.

35
00:02:34,500 --> 00:02:36,100
I lost the Fushi Mirror.

36
00:02:37,060 --> 00:02:38,300
But I still have Bai Ruoxi.

37
00:02:39,620 --> 00:02:41,500
I can still turn this around.

38
00:02:42,900 --> 00:02:43,620
Tomorrow,

39
00:02:44,260 --> 00:02:45,260
you will leave this place.

40
00:02:47,180 --> 00:02:48,140
Are you driving me away?

41
00:02:48,740 --> 00:02:51,100
You're of no use staying here.

42
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:55,820
From now on, that lovesick fool Yuxun
will take care of you.

43
00:03:07,700 --> 00:03:08,940
Wan'er, I'm sorry.

44
00:03:09,980 --> 00:03:11,260
Staying by my side

45
00:03:12,140 --> 00:03:13,900
will only bring you harm.

46
00:03:47,380 --> 00:03:48,860
You finally decide to come back.

47
00:03:50,500 --> 00:03:51,500
I have to say,

48
00:03:51,580 --> 00:03:53,060
after staying here so long,

49
00:03:53,060 --> 00:03:53,940
I can't

50
00:03:53,940 --> 00:03:54,780
sleep anywhere else.

51
00:03:56,500 --> 00:03:57,500
You must be tired from training.

52
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:00,180
Do you want to try this specialty wine
from the Ying clan?

53
00:04:10,700 --> 00:04:11,860
Try it.

54
00:04:17,700 --> 00:04:18,500
This is fine wine.

55
00:04:31,980 --> 00:04:32,540
You drink up.

56
00:04:32,540 --> 00:04:33,900
I'll go make you a few dishes.

57
00:04:36,340 --> 00:04:38,060
Good thing I was clever.

58
00:04:38,060 --> 00:04:39,300
I took the antidote.

59
00:04:39,820 --> 00:04:41,020
This is all I can do to help you.

60
00:05:24,580 --> 00:05:25,980
All things in this world

61
00:05:26,300 --> 00:05:27,660
have their beginning and end.

62
00:05:28,100 --> 00:05:30,460
In the end,
bonds are always shallow and fleeting.

63
00:05:31,340 --> 00:05:32,380
What a pity.

64
00:05:39,660 --> 00:05:41,140
I know that day wasn't a dream.

65
00:05:42,380 --> 00:05:43,500
You really came.

66
00:05:53,860 --> 00:05:55,140
So it really was just a dream.

67
00:06:12,300 --> 00:06:13,100
What are you doing?

68
00:06:15,140 --> 00:06:15,660
Yaoyang,

69
00:06:15,940 --> 00:06:16,700
let me go.

70
00:06:18,540 --> 00:06:19,580
No matter what,

71
00:06:20,500 --> 00:06:21,980
I won't let you become a fiend.

72
00:06:22,740 --> 00:06:23,940
You've done so much for me.

73
00:06:26,100 --> 00:06:27,300
Now it's my turn.

74
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:28,100
What...

75
00:06:28,980 --> 00:06:30,340
What nonsense are you talking about?

76
00:06:31,860 --> 00:06:33,860
You two are really devoted, huh.

77
00:06:34,580 --> 00:06:36,540
Both of you are so eager

78
00:06:36,540 --> 00:06:38,060
to die for the other.

79
00:06:41,860 --> 00:06:42,660
What did you say?

80
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:44,780
She wants to use her remaining soul

81
00:06:44,780 --> 00:06:46,180
to protect your heart meridians.

82
00:06:46,580 --> 00:06:48,100
That way the Gu poison

83
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:49,700
won't kill you.

84
00:06:49,940 --> 00:06:50,740
Understand?

85
00:06:50,860 --> 00:06:51,660
And the cost?

86
00:06:53,140 --> 00:06:55,100
She must become a fiend.

87
00:06:56,260 --> 00:06:57,660
You found out too late.

88
00:06:58,580 --> 00:06:59,820
I'll save

89
00:07:00,460 --> 00:07:01,860
