90
00:07:02,660 --> 00:07:03,660
Stay out of it.

91
00:07:04,740 --> 00:07:07,480
♪What is flickering?♪

92
00:07:07,860 --> 00:07:08,900
You're right.

93
00:07:08,900 --> 00:07:10,220
♪Shining, delicate, and bright♪

94
00:07:11,180 --> 00:07:12,940
I did find out too late.

95
00:07:12,940 --> 00:07:16,220
♪Like a trace of bitterness in a smile♪

96
00:07:16,260 --> 00:07:17,660
♪What is falling?♪

97
00:07:17,660 --> 00:07:18,180
You...

98
00:07:18,860 --> 00:07:19,660
How come?

99
00:07:19,660 --> 00:07:22,340
♪Clean, precise, and light♪

100
00:07:22,380 --> 00:07:23,540
Knowing you,

101
00:07:24,100 --> 00:07:25,740
