102
00:07:26,700 --> 00:07:28,340
You think I want to be here with you?

103
00:07:28,700 --> 00:07:30,300
♪When petals drift down♪

104
00:07:30,340 --> 00:07:31,800
♪When the rain falls all around♪

105
00:07:31,900 --> 00:07:34,500
♪I gaze into your eyes♪

106
00:07:34,660 --> 00:07:36,360
♪Beyond the dunes♪

107
00:07:36,460 --> 00:07:37,740
♪No end in sight♪

108
00:07:37,740 --> 00:07:40,740
♪I am like a mayfly♪

109
00:07:40,900 --> 00:07:42,300
♪I won't ask what the future holds♪

110
00:07:42,340 --> 00:07:43,800
♪Nor will I run away♪

111
00:07:43,820 --> 00:07:46,760
♪Through all seasons by my side♪

112
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:52,020
♪Searching for sparks in the dust♪

113
